[{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":56142,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8404,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":592578,"username":"helphelp","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/helphelp","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1725071f4ec0bd9d0832eb8eddd5f6b6?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1725071f4ec0bd9d0832eb8eddd5f6b6?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1725071f4ec0bd9d0832eb8eddd5f6b6?s=73&d=retro","created":1661675089,"last_modified":1661675089},"last_reply_by":"leonshaw","last_touched":1685241307,"title":"请教一个基础的 Docker 问题，关于容器自动创建文件夹和文件,如图所示","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/943534","created":1685234120,"deleted":0,"content":"首先，在我 Linux 的 home 目录下面，一开始是没有任何的文件夹和文件的\r\n\r\n下面两部分代码，一个是 linuxserver 的 nginx 镜像，一个是官方版\r\n\r\n```\r\ndocker run -d \\\r\n  --name=nginx \\\r\n  -e PUID=1000 \\\r\n  -e PGID=1000 \\\r\n  -e Asia/Shanghai \\\r\n  -p 80:80 \\\r\n  -p 443:443 \\\r\n  -v /home/nginx:/config \\\r\n  --restart unless-stopped \\\r\n  lscr.io/linuxserver/nginx:latest\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\ndocker run -d \\\r\n    --name nginx1 \\\r\n    --log-opt max-size=1m \\\r\n    -v /home/nginx1:/etc/nginx \\\r\n    --restart unless-stopped \\\r\n    nginx\r\n```\r\n\r\n运行之后，\r\n\r\nlinuxserver 会在 /home/nginx 里自动创建文件夹和文件（注意是文件夹和配置文件都自动创建了），\r\n\r\n**而官方版的不会自动创建文件。**\r\n\r\n如图：\r\n![nginx]( https://file.uhsea.com/2305/ca4cd2e176ce4d798b225b4d5e97db6534.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**请问：**\r\n\r\n  **1.为啥官方版的 Nginx 不会自动创建文件呢？**\r\n\r\n  **2.怎么让官方版的自动创建文件呢？就是 nginx.conf 这些配置文件。**","content_rendered":"<p>首先，在我 Linux 的 home 目录下面，一开始是没有任何的文件夹和文件的</p>\n<p>下面两部分代码，一个是 linuxserver 的 nginx 镜像，一个是官方版</p>\n<pre><code>docker run -d \\\n  --name=nginx \\\n  -e PUID=1000 \\\n  -e PGID=1000 \\\n  -e Asia/Shanghai \\\n  -p 80:80 \\\n  -p 443:443 \\\n  -v /home/nginx:/config \\\n  --restart unless-stopped \\\n  lscr.io/linuxserver/nginx:latest\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code>docker run -d \\\n    --name nginx1 \\\n    --log-opt max-size=1m \\\n    -v /home/nginx1:/etc/nginx \\\n    --restart unless-stopped \\\n    nginx\n</code></pre>\n<p>运行之后，</p>\n<p>linuxserver 会在 /home/nginx 里自动创建文件夹和文件（注意是文件夹和配置文件都自动创建了），</p>\n<p><strong>而官方版的不会自动创建文件。</strong></p>\n<p>如图：\n<img alt=\"nginx\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://file.uhsea.com/2305/ca4cd2e176ce4d798b225b4d5e97db6534.png\"/></p>\n<p><strong>请问：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1.为啥官方版的 Nginx 不会自动创建文件呢？</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2.怎么让官方版的自动创建文件呢？就是 nginx.conf 这些配置文件。</strong></p>\n","last_modified":1685234160,"replies":17,"id":943534},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":203888,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3815,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":374049,"username":"Comyn","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Comyn","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/91b2/7ea7/374049_mini.png?m=1684986498","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/91b2/7ea7/374049_normal.png?m=1684986498","