:"v2ex"},"member":{"id":626167,"username":"tit","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tit","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e41/fd9b/626167_mini.png?m=1682573959","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e41/fd9b/626167_normal.png?m=1682573959","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e41/fd9b/626167_large.png?m=1682573959","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e41/fd9b/626167_xlarge.png?m=1682573959","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e41/fd9b/626167_xlarge.png?m=1682573959","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e41/fd9b/626167_xlarge.png?m=1682573959","created":1682573834,"last_modified":1682573959},"last_reply_by":"duke807","last_touched":1685241870,"title":"衰退还会持续多少？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/943546","created":1685239282,"deleted":0,"content":"选大通胀还是大下岗？","content_rendered":"选大通胀还是大下岗？","last_modified":1685239282,"replies":8,"id":943546},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":203888,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3815,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":196767,"username":"lylehust","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lylehust","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f7b4e31b495931d53611c4ddb28e49c3?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f7b4e31b495931d53611c4ddb28e49c3?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f7b4e31b495931d53611c4ddb28e49c3?s=73&d=retro","created":1476758578,"last_modified":1476758578},"last_reply_by":"weijancc","last_touched":1685241499,"title":"请大家帮忙推荐手机","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/943538","created":1685236140,"deleted":0,"content":"本人在美国的公立大学工作。前些天 IT 部门发信：若用自己的手机收发学校的邮件，则手机不能安装微信、QQ 、支付宝，且不能用华为和中兴的手机。\r\n\r\n我现在用的是 Iphone 8+，考虑再买一个手机。人正好回国了，考虑买一个国产手机，有两个方案。\r\n\r\n1. Iphone 8 仍是主力机，再买一个便宜的备用机，专门用来收发学校邮件。\r\n\r\n2. 再买一个现在的主流机型，Iphone 8 专门收发学校邮件。\r\n\r\n因为对国产手机不太熟悉，请大家帮忙推荐。\r\n\r\n方案 1 ，价格 2 千以内，可以是二手机。当然需要靠谱的二手机店。\r\n\r\n方案 2 ，价格 3 千 - 4 千。\r\n\r\n不考虑小米机型，不想折腾去广告。我倾向方案 1 。\r\n\r\n谢谢！","content_rendered":"<p>本人在美国的公立大学工作。前些天 IT 部门发信：若用自己的手机收发学校的邮件，则手机不能安装微信、QQ 、支付宝，且不能用华为和中兴的手机。</p>\n<p>我现在用的是 Iphone 8+，考虑再买一个手机。人正好回国了，考虑买一个国产手机，有两个方案。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Iphone 8 仍是主力机，再买一个便宜的备用机，专门用来收发学校邮件。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>再买一个现在的主流机型，Iphone 8 专门收发学校邮件。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>因为对国产手机不太熟悉，请大家帮忙推荐。</p>\n<p>方案 1 ，价格 2 千以内，可以是二手机。当然需要靠谱的二手机店。</p>\n<p>方案 2 ，价格 3 千 - 4 千。</p>\n<p>不考虑小米机型，不想折腾去广告。我倾向方案 1 。</p>\n<p>谢谢！</p>\n","last_modified":1685236140,"replies":8,"id":943538},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":203888,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3815,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":88339,"username":"kangyue9999","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kangyue9999","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b91fdbb9604d65e2e7ef5e6ec722b2a6?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b91fdbb9604d65e2e7ef5e6ec722b2a6?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b91fdbb9604d65e2e7ef5e6ec722b2a6?s=73&d=retro","created":1419480947,"la